      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING ELI (2) last start finished 4th over 352m at this track beaten 8 lengths (20.31) behind Golden Legs in a Maiden on February 18. Expected to go close with a clean break. ORIGINALITY (1) boxed on the inside and gets chance to find form. Last time finished 5th on February 11 over 352m at this track behind Electric Luxe beaten 5.5 lengths (20.67) in a Maiden. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Can measure up this time. LAKODA MILEY (4) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Smashing Double (20.20) in a Maiden. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Expected to feature again. PRETTY MISS (8) is a David Harvey-trained newcomer by Fernando Bale out of Miss Wanted. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can sneak into the frame at her first appearance.",
